@baseUrl = http://localhost:4100/api
@authToken = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Create a New Property Listing (Draft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Luxury 3 Bed Apartment in Manchester",
  "description": "Stunning tenanted apartment in the heart of Manchester city center with stable rental yield.",
  "propertyType": "flat",
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "bathrooms": 2,
  "location": "Manchester",
  "postcode": "M1 1AD",
  "tenure": "leasehold",
  "status": "published",
  "heroImage": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?q=80",
  "gallery": [
    {
      "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?q=80",
      "alt": "Beautiful living area"
    }
  ],
  "investmentMetrics": {
    "askingPrice": 250000,
    "monthlyRent": 1500,
    "leaseYearsRemaining": 125
  },
  "serviceCharge": 120,
  "groundRent": 20,
  "councilTaxBand": "C",
  "tenented": true,
  "tenancyStatus": "Active AST",
  "contractType": "ast",
  "rentCollectionStatus": "agent-managed",
  "arrearsStatus": "no-arrears",
  "tenancyNotes": "Reliable tenant since 2024",
  "epc": "B",
  "floorplans": [
    "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502672260266-1c1ef2d93688?q=80"
  ]
}

### 2. Create another Property (Different parameters for sorting)
POST {{baseUrl}}/properties
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cosy 1 Bed Studio in Liverpool",
  "description": "High yield studio listing close to universities.",
  "propertyType": "flat",
  "bedrooms": 1,
  "bathrooms": 1,
  "location": "Liverpool",
  "postcode": "L3 5AA",
  "tenure": "freehold",
  "status": "published",
  "heroImage": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?q=80",
  "investmentMetrics": {
    "askingPrice": 100000,
    "monthlyRent": 800
  },
  "councilTaxBand": "A",
  "tenented": true,
  "tenancyStatus": "Active"
}

### 3. Search Properties - All Published
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties

### 4. Search Properties - Liverpool only
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?location=Liverpool

### 5. Search Properties - Sort by Highest Yield
# Liverpool studio should rank higher than Manchester (9.6% vs 7.2%)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?sortBy=Highest Yield

### 6. Search Properties - Sort by Lowest Price
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?sortBy=Lowest Price

### 7. Get Property Details (Replace with generated slug or ID)
# Use slug format generated on save e.g. luxury-3-bed-apartment-in-manchester-xxxxx
@propertySlug = luxury-3-bed-apartment-in-manchester-
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertySlug}}

### 8. Update Property Listing (Update status to under-offer)
# Replace the ID below with a real MongoDB ObjectId from creation
@propertyId = 654e56789abcdef012345678
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "under-offer",
  "investmentMetrics": {
    "askingPrice": 245000
  }
}

### 9. Delete a Property
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/properties/{{propertyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### ==========================================
### LEAD SUBMISSIONS & ROUTING MULTIPLEXER
### ==========================================

### 10. Submit a General Enquiry Lead
POST {{baseUrl}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "janesmith@example.com",
  "phone": "+447123456789",
  "type": "General Enquiry",
  "message": "I would like to speak to your concierge team regarding selling my portfolio."
}

### 11. Submit a Property Enquiry Lead (Requires propertyId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Harrison",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "type": "Property Enquiry",
  "message": "Is this property still available?",
  "metadata": {
    "propertyId": "654e56789abcdef012345678"
  }
}

### 12. Submit a Mortgage Lead (Multiplexed to Partner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Green",
  "email": "alice.green@example.com",
  "phone": "+447890123456",
  "type": "Mortgage Lead",
  "metadata": {
    "budget": 200000,
    "intent": "Buy-to-Let Mortgage"
  }
}

### 13. Submit an Insurance Lead (Multiplexed to Partner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie Brown",
  "email": "charlie@example.com",
  "type": "Insurance Lead",
  "metadata": {
    "structuralRequirements": "Standard brick construction with slate roof, tenanted residential block."
  }
}

### 14. Submit a Property Valuation Lead (Multiplexed to Partner)
POST {{baseUrl}}/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Diane Prince",
  "email": "diane@example.com",
  "type": "Valuation Lead",
  "metadata": {
    "propertyAddress": "123 High Street, London, EC1A 1BB"
  }
}

### 15. List Leads (Concierge Dashboard view)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leads
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 16. Get Lead Details
@leadId = 654e56789abcdef012345679
GET {{baseUrl}}/leads/{{leadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 17. Update Lead Status (Triage status updates)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/leads/{{leadId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Contacted",
  "message": "Contacted via phone, scheduling viewing."
}
